{"data": {"node": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3910010955788003", "organization": {"id": "514462403203330", "viewer_permissions": [], "application_groupings": {"nodes": [{"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "4486563551434692"}]}, "id": "295311585777083"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "3910010955788003"}]}, "id": "886090098646518"}]}}, "firstRevision": {"nodes": [{"application": {"id": "3910010955788003", "release_date": 1627928575, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7954465584675833"}, "id": "1457488524585046"}]}}, "binary": null, "live_binary": null, "created_date": 1723128833, "id": "7785838711538522", "is_initial_release": false, "name_with_fallback": "v10", "pdp_metadata_with_fallback": {"version": 10, "application": {"is_concept": false, "latest_released_pdp_metadata": {"id": "7785842044871522"}, "release_status": "RELEASED", "id": "3910010955788003"}, "id": "7785842044871522", "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "release_date": 1723446654, "administration_status": "APPROVED", "is_first": false, "release_status": "RELEASED", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "3910010955788003", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "1259746821094145"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "PostOculusStore_FreeToPlay.png", "id": "844627027575279", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75297582_844627030908612_100519495280906896_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cAmnJ4OFA2kQ7kNvgGrZrL_&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBik8FVWrya21FHYt_sO4ApCKQUPKhHhQ11gMZPp2xQDA&oe=66E5826D"}]}, "id": "3703478143313678", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Volleggball", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# \ud83d\udd25\ud83c\udfd0\ud83e\udd5a Smashez avant d'\u00eatre cuit ! \ud83e\udd5a\ud83c\udfd0\ud83d\udd25\n\nPr\u00e9parez-vous \u00e0 vous fendre la coquille avec Volleggball, le jeu de volleyball qui vous fera sauter d'oeuf-orie ! \n\nCette eggsp\u00e9rience multijoueur n'est pas pour les poules mouill\u00e9es - c'est une aventure digne des meilleurs omelettes qui vous donnera envie d'y revenir encore et encore !\n\n{844627027575279}\n\n## \ud83d\udc23 Mettez tous vos amis dans le m\u00eame panier \ud83d\udc23 \n\nRejoignez des parties ouvertes et amusez-vous avec des joueurs du monde oeuf-tier, sans vous brouiller (ou pas) !\n\n## \ud83d\udc50 Un gameplay \u00e0 la coque \ud83d\udc50\n\nChoisissez entre des matchs simple ou doubles pour une dose parfaite de comp-oeuf-tition.\n\n## \ud83e\udd5aDes adversaires IA coquasse\ud83e\udd5a\n\nAffrontez des rob\u0153ufs dr\u00f4les et maladroits qui vous feront rire \u00e0 vous en secouer le jaune.\n\n## \ud83d\ude0e Personnalisations \u0153ufs-riginales\ud83d\ude0e \n\nD\u00e9marquez-vous avec des dizaines de fa\u00e7ons de personnaliser votre avacoque.\n\n## \ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f Environnements coquetiers\ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f \n\nFaites des smashes \u00e0 travers 4 cartes incroyables :\n- Paradis tropical\n- Splendeur automnale au bord du lac\n- Merveille hivernale en montagne\n- Enfer volcanique (attention \u00e0 ne pas vous faire cuire !)\n\n\ud83d\udd25\ud83c\udfd0\ud83e\udd5a\n\nQue vous soyez un pro aguerri ou un d\u00e9butant, Volleggball offre une exp\u00e9rience de volleyball egg-citante qui va vous endurcir le blanc ! Alors ne marchez pas sur des oeufs - attrapez vos amis et pr\u00e9parez-vous \u00e0 battre la concurrence dans cette aventure de volleyball egg-ceptionnelle !\n\n\ud83e\udd5a\ud83c\udfd0\ud83d\udd25\n\n---\n\ud83c\udf99\ufe0fDiscutez avec nous sur notre Discord !\nhttps://discord.gg/NvRjfSnmma\n\n", "short_description": "Le meilleur joeuf de volleyball dans ce monde \u00e0 la coque"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "PostOculusStore_FreeToPlay.png", "id": "1045102036463669", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75361353_1045102039797002_7060094311243211613_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=RegjiPSyM_MQ7kNvgEWdQmT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCh128asPHh14AVhgCC0qaPNwUfTtadRqmLIdzD5uKekA&oe=66E55EAA"}, {"file_name": "Customization.png", "id": "796479432600979", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982566_796479435934312_1716921857363409735_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0Lt89AiIZC8Q7kNvgFZ0nRS&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAHOpIhiyEAt4BEKo5jjzvGlSMHVDqtivvFzDXIu6SjaQ&oe=66E57746"}, {"file_name": "NEWVolcanoMap.png", "id": "385364441226303", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031362_385364444559636_8957833416117844976_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=J2cIFKGlPVIQ7kNvgG9KQX5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAz_gXzM0R6tN4Fg3sRd-h9L5hncCISpQIos0uQtYoWxw&oe=66E56F8C"}, {"file_name": "PostOculusStore_Volleggball.png", "id": "1682716595888004", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035315_1682716599221337_7075827842099927230_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sgIpQK6CdKMQ7kNvgGS-g1q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDIFwUtnfi0MLjS8zugRCGU3i1wT-kDXnbi82zW1j2uhQ&oe=66E5627A"}, {"file_name": "Cover_Square.png", "id": "1421672538303890", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75210390_1421672541637223_4430522060750231209_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4_Fkqc_z3WoQ7kNvgEzVcTV&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBd66--9ErlgVcE3kbHI9hfKOPPSwftYU3EIH5Dzx-seA&oe=66E565E9"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "939222280086458", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57575358_939222283419791_5003080023397223869_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WiDrR0LGy0sQ7kNvgFVX9t8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBT4z7KQnhlwDzVFBWGQtH0WyBpoi3YXFec2JxUy_OV4w&oe=66E57BEC"}, {"file_name": "SideQuest_FreeToPlay_upscale_3000-900.png", "id": "827459426004661", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031489_827459429337994_7170894236114491165_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=w1dW1izgWMoQ7kNvgFQxt5j&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA_3xS2nMNk-IwSBx8qbKlKy6EgxQIPVYtfUr6nY4M7WA&oe=66E55718"}, {"file_name": "OculusStore_FreeToPlay_1080-360.png", "id": "499669695875202", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036618_499669699208535_9131822356516957432_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7dhdVvg7r5sQ7kNvgHpriTH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBYdKsVDQFqnW4S-o-dg64YoNI9kRRYOd9i55HIqDvm0w&oe=66E58DC4"}, {"file_name": "Logo 1120-1425.png", "id": "410885247147896", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031495_410885250481229_4836999270457677486_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WvYClb6jGqMQ7kNvgHnwaPP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCq7js6_suP9m0nvko81VD31d7Mj38GztZ_qclBGPSaOg&oe=66E5765D"}, {"file_name": "Cover_Portrait.png", "id": "348869883892135", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001726_348869887225468_2871228655726821519_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AgtzhvWCkb8Q7kNvgFvWG_Q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCkaaktUwC_SNyCedRmSinmMxQNbhXDaMrJvX25AtpEhQ&oe=66E58D57"}]}, "id": "2245259855853432", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "PostOculusStore_FreeToPlay.png", "id": "1552696538557236", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974515_1552696541890569_5347462861699962584_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uz9pDdkDzFYQ7kNvgH_xuFX&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDDUE8oRu8EIDnzpMpmjjvpz9Tfr_Y2RYFQOK7Am424Cw&oe=66E57401"}, {"file_name": "PostOculusStore_NewContent.png", "id": "921346419069217", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035326_921346422402550_6850587611098269896_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xHhl_cl8ebIQ7kNvgF0s4T-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDen72BgdLEvv_EtUvingdUgfVJcZ0OLZXUJXOt8WqnZg&oe=66E584B4"}, {"file_name": "PostOculusStore_FreeYolkies.png", "id": "933413718102958", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003247_933413721436291_435652226654268995_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7HBtcg-DvToQ7kNvgGBSV_6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAaEO-6kjxWioF4GYcGkDDofRZDAv0XC1PYauXoGz36iQ&oe=66E57DCB"}, {"file_name": "com.pinkmarmot.VirtualVolley-20211203-145600_Moment3 (1).png", "id": "255208209930803", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974613_255208216597469_559092475689458136_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1P1brhRcD78Q7kNvgEr5Vfp&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCe_txg-uxF5Vdn-CfuiACcsQ9oroGi-V_cgNXMrnmHVw&oe=66E57214"}, {"file_name": "com.pinkmarmot.VirtualVolley-20211203-150103_Moment2 (1).png", "id": "320468449691304", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031379_320468456357970_3230564276216986875_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ExBX7ZYLGY4Q7kNvgEgcyqF&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCMMk0FeH-En-n8xokuuzKiwN4BI8NqQU0-0VyWYUCWfw&oe=66E56DD2"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "PostOculusStore_Volleggball.png", "id": "3722721384723693", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974611_3722721391390359_3140296778754052086_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=r8X-ef7xwEkQ7kNvgGZwPgu&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBecd6GQvY_MMOuIibQV4WRJDSpts-7uvfM_5CQ3FkKTQ&oe=66E55F0D"}, "display_name": "Volleggball", "keywords": ["volleyball", "sport", "coop", "competitive", "multiplayer"], "long_description": "# \ud83d\udd25\ud83c\udfd0\ud83e\udd5a Spike before you get cooked ! \ud83e\udd5a\ud83c\udfd0\ud83d\udd25\n\nGet ready to crack up with Volleggball, the egg-citing volleyball game that'll have you jump for victory! \n\nThis yolk-tastic multiplayer experience is no chicken feed \u2013 it's a shell-shocking adventure that'll keep you coming back for more!\n\n{1045102036463669}\n\n## \ud83d\udc23 Scramble with your friends\ud83d\udc23 \n\nJump into open lobbies and get cracking with players from around the globe!\n\n## \ud83d\udc50 Sunny-side up gameplay \ud83d\udc50\n\nChoose between 1vs1 or 2vs2 matches for the perfect serving of competition\n\n## \ud83e\udd5aHilarious AI Opponents\ud83e\udd5a\n\nFace off against funny, clumsy egg bots that'll keep you laughing as you play\n\n## \ud83d\ude0e Egg-spressive customization \ud83d\ude0e \n\nStand out from the carton with dozens of ways to personalize your egg-vatar\n\n## \ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f Eggs-quisite environments \ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f\n\nSpike your way through 4 egg-mazing maps: \n- Tropical Island Paradise\n- Autumn Lake Splendor\n- Winter Mountain Wonderland\n- Volcanic Inferno (careful not to get poached!)\n\n\ud83d\udd25\ud83c\udfd0\ud83e\udd5a\n\nWhether you're a seasoned pro or just out of your shell, Volleggball offers an egg-citing VR experience that's no yolk! So don't chicken out \u2013 grab your friends and get ready to scramble the competition in this egg-ceptional volleyball adventure!\n\n\ud83e\udd5a\ud83c\udfd0\ud83d\udd25\n\n---\n\ud83c\udf99\ufe0fChat with us on our discord ! https://discord.gg/NvRjfSnmma\n", "short_description": "Best volleyball game in the